===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 65 people, 27 households, and 21 families residing in the city. The median age was 45.3 years. For every 100 females there were 91.2 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 77.8 males age 18 and over. All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A21675&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A21675&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A21675&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

The [[population density]] was 190.4 inhabitants per square mile (73.5/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 33 housing units at an average density of 96.7 per square mile (37.3/km<sup>2</sup>), of which 18.2% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 20.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

Of the 27 households, 29.6% had children under the age of 18 living with them; 55.6% were [[Marriage|married couples]] living together; 7.4% were cohabitating couples; 29.6% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present; and 7.4% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present. Of all households, 22.2% were non-families, 11.1% were made up of individuals, and 7.4% had someone living alone who was 65 years old or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

26.2% of residents were under the age of 18, and 27.7% of residents were under the age of 20; 3.1% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 18.5% were from 25 to 44; 29.2% were from 45 to 64; and 21.5% were 65 years of age or older. The gender makeup of the city was 47.7% male and 52.3% female.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

